{"tid":2386931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：公務員能否持BNO與反制措施不能混為一談","createTime":"2021-01-30T02:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T04:25:45.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"eb782f9adf46e7efd2c7cfcc6b7c97a0517346aa","tid":2386931,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】英國政府明日起接受擁有英國國民（海外），即BNO身份的香港人申請居留簽證。中國外交部宣布，同日開始不再承認BNO護照作為身份證明及旅行證件。公務員事務局局長聶德權指，公務員能否持有BNO，會按現行法例處理，認為不能將外交部針對BNO的反制措施混為一談。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權：「特區政府已表明BNO不再作為旅遊證件及作為身份證明，會按此去執行。至於公務員本身擁有國籍的安排，會跟基本法及香港法例現有規定進行，我相信不能將兩事混為一談。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=422275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422275&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=b2996ff4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422275&h=e52bf15e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=422275</a>"},{"pid":"326eb1f942dcdac2ee05128e826b74da324ac7b0","tid":2386931,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:31:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">釋放胡志偉</span>"},{"pid":"dbd8ae289ee64a752bcd1d137114ceaee69d7bde","tid":2386931,"uid":77196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:31:55.000Z","msg":"吓，因為你班狗官大部份都有BNO所以唔敢跟機？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6edfce606050bff75f4a0d030ecf186de403c5","tid":2386931,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:32:08.000Z","msg":"手持外國護照<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"4932ac95c400a40cddefc3209fa2ba038767442a","tid":2386931,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbd8ae289ee64a752bcd1d137114ceaee69d7bde","tid":2386931,"uid":77196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:31:55.000Z","msg":"吓，因為你班狗官大部份都有BNO所以唔敢跟機？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:32:43.000Z","msg":"佢地其實有BC 多"},{"pid":"1cfb63f3168dcce4c258cfba57b6887cab36b89b","tid":2386931,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:34:14.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"> 只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 會引致戰爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"6db0e16572bda3bd89ba33e9fab1e4197258a767","tid":2386931,"uid":6435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbd8ae289ee64a752bcd1d137114ceaee69d7bde","tid":2386931,"uid":77196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:31:55.000Z","msg":"吓，因為你班狗官大部份都有BNO所以唔敢跟機？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:35:09.000Z","msg":"有外國國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567aac9e09a2c4e472334cc3e190c1b6eda1b969","tid":2386931,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:35:14.000Z","msg":"得就得，唔得就唔得<br />\n不過禁得BNO就唔該禁埋其他外國護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cc4bd68322f253257ce1dd486d45a20203789e","tid":2386931,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:44:27.000Z","msg":"你淆底"},{"pid":"1f5fe59b5e2acd5cc6adaaebcbb5cff5a3cc128e","tid":2386931,"uid":68231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:44:41.000Z","msg":"即係公務員繼續可以有BNO 或外國國籍？"},{"pid":"3225ab34b702e374d6a95540bf4d3ed3c68a9087","tid":2386931,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:50:03.000Z","msg":"公務員 / 政治團隊唔計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c91ffa6a20c87cfa663599382f1c53c4c28923b","tid":2386931,"uid":22554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbd8ae289ee64a752bcd1d137114ceaee69d7bde","tid":2386931,"uid":77196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:31:55.000Z","msg":"吓，因為你班狗官大部份都有BNO所以唔敢跟機？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:57:53.000Z","msg":"去到佢個年資, 而且又曾經係AO, 點會係BNO, 要攞都攞BC 啦"},{"pid":"ea34d2bd9df906dac0a24592bf85f152c5b52de5","tid":2386931,"uid":296830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">三耳焗腸只是一隻哈巴狗搖尾乞憐討北、西廠公公歡心。焗腸記唔記得某年四月震驚世界一晚三改新聞稿事件呀！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=